MISCELLANEOUS ORDERS

2011-0191. Disciplinary Counsel v. Jones.

This matter is before the court upon Thomas Jones’s filing of a motion to quash subpoena and/or motion for protective order. Upon consideration thereof, it is ordered that the motion to quash and/or for protective order is denied.

This matter is also before the court upon Jones’s filing of a motion to strike Disciplinary Counsel’s memorandum in opposition to the motion to quash subpoena and/or for protective order. Upon consideration thereof, the motion to strike is denied.
